Been a while, but I'm back.  The way you worded this is erroneous.  It makes it sound like it's consistantly minimum backstab damage after you have Chaotic Stab.<br>
<br>
&quot;Chaotic Stab: (1 skill level - cost 6 skill points) - This ability allows the Rogue to do his minimum backstab damage on any backstab attempt, even if that attempt is not made while behind the opponent.&quot;<br>
<br>
I think you should say &quot;This ability allows the Rogue to do his minimum backstab damage when attempting to backstab while not actually behind the opponent.&quot;<br>
